Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer vacation is so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:16.78,test2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H907664&\fscx165\fscy191.25\pos(260,406)\frz16.854}Rehearsal!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.78,0:00:18.28,test2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx241.25\fscy275\c&H967564&\pos(493,378)\frx358\fry354}Rehearsal!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get all the desks pushed to the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Yano's in the bathroom or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's from Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't make it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.72,0:00:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:42.73,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\pos(221,354)\fscx101.25\fscy136.25\c&HB0B0BE&}Sorry. I can't make it to rehearsal today,\N so get some to stand in for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:42.73,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I can't make it to rehearsal today, so get some to stand in for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't even start without the lead! Call him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've turned off his cell phone. It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has no sense of responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. He'll get things done when they need to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the real problem here...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... and I was looking forward to today, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:16.88,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:22.85,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:28.98,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:34.94,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:42.33,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:47.04,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:52.96,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:02:01.85,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:06.77,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:13.90,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:20.66,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:16.88,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:22.85,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:28.98,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:34.94,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:42.33,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:47.04,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:52.96,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:02:01.85,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:06.77,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:13.90,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:20.66,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:34.96,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,800)\pos(140,384)}Episode 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:34.96,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, Yano didn't come to the rehearsal after that, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Mizu-chin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll totally go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna wear a yukata?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also invited Yano and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He skips out on practice, but he always shows up at times like these...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once he shows up, I'll really let him have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! Get my yukata out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're wearing a yukata too, Nana!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry for being so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, you look really cute today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That yukata suits you surprisingly well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That color is perfect for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is it really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I borrowed it from my cousin's older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pattern on mine was just too childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your cheeks look really cute, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's apricot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you just got out of bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! They're wearing yukatas! The yukata brigade is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:34.56,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,The boys are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, about that... we haven't been able to reach his cell at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think he will... but probably with his local friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We might run into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice... if he makes it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Takahashi, you look completely different!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was telling her! Doesn't she look good in a yukata?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They do say that baby-faced kids unexpectedly look good in classic Japanese clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to the normal you, Takahashi, you look like a heron tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... such a waste. If only yukatas had been the school uniform, I might've been so popular...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, geez! Yano, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, they said they'd still give you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeuchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you surprised me! I wasn't sure who it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you here with?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here with some classmates. What about you, Takeuchi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people from my neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's... not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I wasn't implying that or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano couldn't make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy just doesn't seem to need other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it very well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...no matter how much we talk about something, he doesn't budge an inch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we're not reaching him or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes it seems so futile...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just feel like whatever we do will be useless in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I got really excited and even wore a yukata...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...counted down the days to the rehearsals on my fingers...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it all feels so useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, want a snow cone? I'll go buy some!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, looks like I can't get in touch with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to complain about how he skipped out on the rehearsals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was... the anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day before yesterday, for Nana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be pretty harsh, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... didn't know at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just getting all festive, without knowing a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having someone always excited and happy around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long you keep your spirits high, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look cute in that yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.71,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA6A298&\fscx437.5\fscy342.5\move(327,308,326,12,0,1570)}Yano
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's a stalker! She's loitering in front of my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:06:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm no stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That caught me off guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long has he been watching me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had some business with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aimlessly lingering around my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I refuse degenerates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...! Yano, open the gate, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The female pervert stalker has gone berserk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a moron?! Mrs. Yano, I've come for a school visit with your stupid-ass son!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to have kept you waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... the worst possible situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay as long as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all alone with Yano in his room...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm getting nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi, why did you come poking around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I th-th-thought you m-might be sick, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you think I was sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, like, you've missed every rehearsal so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you just get right to the point and ask why I've missed them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are one to speak right now, since you're the one who missed them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you miss them, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been drowning in my memories of Nana-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no good in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can I skip the rehearsal the day after tomorrow, and the one two days after tomorrow, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you miss them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer break, and you expect me to wake up at nine in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my own fault for worrying about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got to eat some bean jelly, so don't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I come here just to eat bean jelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then don't eat any!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll eat some!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...? He's totally cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And.. I finally got to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:09:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, is that a photo album?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec. I'll take out all the bad pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "bad"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was your middle school trip to Sapporo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... can I see a picture of Nana-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do after looking at something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even sure... what I want to do after I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty careless, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize where you are right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But the door's open, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The window, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are passing by outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're my classmate, Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't done anything. She just fell on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry for making such a fuss...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a moron? Don't take me so seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that... is that just it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this isn't a picture of Nana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a single picture of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't budge an inch....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought of you every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to rehearsal all excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got really happy wore a yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even come over your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But none of that seems to matter to you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better be at rehearsal the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I could say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just another classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just... wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, you may not have someone left who you really, really love...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and that might be a really sad thing for you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:11:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because there are people out there who really, really love you, shouldn't it all equal out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... please don't think you're all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm watching you, so..!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always watching you, so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always watching over you, so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for having bothered you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always watching you... I'm always watching over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... please don't think you're all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you check on the props?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going pretty well so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because Yamamoto-san's so reliable for things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not here again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's come to this, I'll just have to cover with my acting skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But really, nothing's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... so powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:11:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He... showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, the happi coats.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I borrowed some samples.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which color would be better?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think red's pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I thought so, too. Red's better, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It really does look cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this way, dirt won't stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The red looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're totally going with white.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other person who can make my heart beat this fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is white all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The white suits you. It must be nice, Yano. Everything looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked good, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in that yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talkin--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeuchi sent it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took a pretty good picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I regretted not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you're watching me, didn't you? Always watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I.. I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about that "it all equals out" junk? As if that logic works!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're watching over me? Spewing out a guy line like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really conceited, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mean, saying it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me borrow your chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise to always watch over you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:03.44,tab.,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1200,0)\alpha&H30&\fscx151.25\fscy150\c&HFFFFFF&\frx10\fry358\frz3.974\move(348,317,347,90,0,4696)}September 4th\N\N Helpers:\N\N Mizuguchi\N\N Miyamoto
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer break flew by in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's been no change between me and Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty impressive that Yano can fall asleep in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's using my bag as a pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he's dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some airheaded dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of dreams Yano has...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Yamamoto's older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geh! That guy with her is Kagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you mean that guy who skipped out of our grade and graduated?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always with a different girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really going out with a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He threw his water on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a battlefield?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.99,0:14:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys are in the same class as Yuri, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but could you lend me some cash?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left without paying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you put that much Tabasco on, you'll get hemorrhoids!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:14:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hemorrhoids, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't resemble your younger sister much, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you think I'm some kind of idiot, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ah, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever he's in bad mood, it always turns out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can be such a kid at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your boyfriend doesn't have the best reputation, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't he so cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His bad parts are part of his charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no perfect man out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I can understand him, that's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They call that sort of thing "being blind."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't really fallen in love with anyone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They call people like you "immature know-it-alls."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and fall in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is Nana-san waiting for her boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She should wait in a warmer place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has no cash. If she sees us, she'll probably try to sponge us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you wanna do today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to your place, Takeuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, could I change first?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the new Sunday's out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? It looks so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could really laugh at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still think he's gonna come?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you waiting around?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To gather my rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your rage...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gather my rage and curse him to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate women.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a hand warmer. It's a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says not to talk to other guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but if I respond with "didn't you have sex with that other girl?" things really get messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He completely enjoys every minute of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I cry, he says "I've made another girl cry" all arrogantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That jerk can just die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should fall off a bridge, break his neck, fall headfirst into a dump truck and smash his head, and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:16:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must think I'm some kind of moron, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... what do you think I should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Figure out your own problems by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm a moron, I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could tell you, but in exchange, you better do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it make me happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably something where no ones cries or gets yelled at.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where no one gets hit or has stuff thrown at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then.. why don't we both go searching for our own happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That's a bean jelly bun! Trade with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's half.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really let him have it when I broke up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You'll definitely regret this later!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serves him right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness is a hot chocolate on a cold days!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still people around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. They're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this will become a memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're seen by anyone, it'll become a huge fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I graduated today, I don't really care.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have another year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll only make you look even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. It's cold and it stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! Take me to the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it stinks like kelp! It wasn't supposed to be like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! A bug! Over here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gross, gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back! Let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back! Let's go back! Let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mocchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motoharu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to see something beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll take you to the southern islands one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, first I have to save crazy money... So about ten years, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.83,0:19:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I get us something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is coffee all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bumped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still seeing him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only met with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I only met with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagawa, a junior is here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A junior?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if, you moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you win or lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winning and losing doesn't matter in these kinds of situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept on punching until I was satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means you were also punched until he was satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Don't touch them, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I wanna take a picture of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you an idiot or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be proof that you fought for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As that arrogant guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like crying, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no human out there who likes crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm here like this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you absolutely won't betray me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no second chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely won't betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Motoharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down and listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see... Nana-san was riding with Kagawa in his car, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.14,0:22:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.64,0:22:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.61,0:22:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... sorry. I was using your bag as a pillow?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've just woken me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you looked like you were having a happy dream, so I didn't want to wake you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.37,0:22:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A happy dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.95,0:22:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.16,0:22:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happiness...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.46,0:22:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.71,0:22:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.42,0:22:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.97,0:22:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Something warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something warm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Like a steamed meat bun or a roasted sweet potato.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that warms you up on a cold day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:22:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that soothes your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:22:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A steamed meat bun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.94,0:23:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it can be anything, like a book you like or a CD.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or someone you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go get some steamed meat buns.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already the season for steamed meat buns?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the first time I wished for someone else's happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.96,0:23:05.61,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuhi kage wo hosoku nobashita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:10.82,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro wo fukaku somete yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.82,0:23:17.50,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitto saigo no jikan da to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:23.92,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Namida koraeteta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:30.93,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Omoide nante itsumo kanashisugiru bakari
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:37.43,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Isso wasurete shimaitai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.43,0:23:44.15,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Nido to aenai kimi no senka to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:49.95,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Saigo no yuuhi mitsumetsudzuketa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.95,0:23:57.12,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Sotto sotto koboreochiteiku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.12,0:24:06.17,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Ima wa kono ame ni utare
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.17,0:24:12.09,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Mou naite ii ka na
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.09,0:24:14.72,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi wa inai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.72,0:24:21.23,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Namida afuretemo tomenaide ite
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.23,0:24:27.90,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Ame yo koorasete kokoro made
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.90,0:24:37.49,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Sotto kono mama kiete shimaitai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.76,0:25:01.27,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the sunset ima wa utawanaideite
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.27,0:25:07.94,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Umi ni ochiteyuku kanashii iro ne
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.94,0:25:14.66,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Zutto kono basho de hitori ni sasete
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.66,0:25:24.04,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuhi yo kono mama shizumanaide ite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.96,0:23:05.61,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The sunset stretches my shadow long and thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:10.82,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Its colors deeply dye my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.82,0:23:17.50,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,When you said this was probably the last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:23.92,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I held back my tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:30.93,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Memories are always too sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:37.43,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to forget them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.43,0:23:44.15,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I continued to watch the last sunset
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:49.95,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and your back that I would never see again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.95,0:23:57.12,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun that slowly, slowly sets in the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.12,0:24:06.17,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm being drenched by this rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.17,0:24:12.09,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right if I cry now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.09,0:24:14.79,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no longer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.79,0:24:21.23,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if my tears begin to overflow, don't stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.23,0:24:27.90,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain, freeze me down to my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.90,0:24:37.49,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to silently fade into nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.76,0:25:01.27,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the sunset. Don't sing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.27,0:25:07.94,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun casts sad colors as it sinks into the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.94,0:25:14.66,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me stay here alone forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.66,0:25:24.04,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it so the sun never sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.91,0:25:34.94,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HDC6CE3&\c&HFDE2FF&\pos(450,377)\fscx93.75\fscy122.5}Episode 4 Preview ...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.52,0:25:07.36,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it my imagination...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.36,0:25:11.86,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,...or has the person\N I like seemed distant lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.86,0:25:15.99,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day we had\N the steamed meat buns together.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.99,0:25:19.99,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be\N so protective of me like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.99,0:25:20.83,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.58,0:25:24.33,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.33,0:25:28.71,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll be\N able to talk like we did before...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.71,0:25:31.09,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll only say this once, so listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.46,0:25:34.38,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
